{"tid":1792373,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[鬼滅。紅蓮華改］ 《黑紫荊》","createTime":"2019-12-21T15:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T08:33:32.000Z","uid":341746,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cfbfd1e5e89c2a2f3e9af0527fb3c75db6f75c7c","tid":1792373,"uid":341746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:01:18.000Z","msg":"［鬼滅紅蓮華］抗爭改詞  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望幫手足打打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FE40N7DOPAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFE40N7DOPAQ&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3BSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=cb745ace\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FE40N7DOPAQ</a><br />\n<br />\n巴絲打多多指教, 幫手改改<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是非歪理嘲諷 眼眸也都通紅 <br />\n無退縮英勇大眾<br />\n冒險街裏指控 莫須有監察罪責的重<br />\n拒靜默送中<br />\n<br />\n血色染紅了天空 <br />\n覺醒美夢告終<br />\n缺少怪俠那英勇 無異能自身都出眾<br />\n劫難內變種<br />\n<br />\n畏懼裏挫敗裏無瑟縮的理據<br />\n讓我可為理想再去追 <br />\n<br />\n無邪的<br />\n迎著槍火去抵擋 同齊步牽手去奔往<br />\n從囚禁裏亡魂裏 真理不朽之火茁壯<br />\n劃破漆黑 燃亮著盼望<br />\n<br />\n何時起<br />\n圍捕書生有不安 同衛校院都有不當<br />\n懸崖岩石亦開花黑紫荊綻放<br />\n照遍香港 見曙光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caeab2121b6fb1205b4b91281e4d2c7425cfde0e","tid":1792373,"uid":341746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"推  <br />\n光復<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c496ba41bb51abeb16021fdc4b0e8ecb591f8ce4","tid":1792373,"uid":341746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"